<br>
A caster is limited by both mana and aggro.  We could do damage quicker but then we would end up dead from aggro and even if we didn't die we would be OOM.  There doesn't seem to be a practical application of the quick damage principle that allows casters to outdamage rogues without dying.  Poor mages don't even have any aggro reducing spells!  The only real limitation you have on rogues is how many you can reasonably get behind a mob for backstabbing.  That certainly isn't going to be a problem in an exp group. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=101939"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Atri Drumrunner</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.eqdiva.com/"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:darkblue;">Virtuoso</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:darkblue;">Erollisi Marr</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=191240"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Cameiel Stormgate</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.graffe.com/"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:darkred;">Sorcerer</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR E