<br>
From the perspective of a low 50's wiz, mana regen does not limit my dps nearly as much as aggro.  Without all those AA you probably have (and yes, I still desperately need concussion), I cannot do significantly more dps than the melee without getting aggro and causing more trouble than its worth for the group.  <br>
